its all your Fluke test tools and accessories. Configure the diced foam interior to store, protect, and carry your test tools.', '<div id=\"specification_content\"><div class=\"clickability\"><table><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"2\">Specifications</td></tr><tr><td style=\"width: 35%;\">Dimensions (HxWxD)</td><td>13.5 in x 18.3 in x 7 in (34.3 cm x 46.5 cm x 17.8 cm)</td></tr><tr><td>Waterproof depth</td><td>0.9 m (3 ft)</td></tr><tr><td>Safety certifications</td><td>IP67 rated<br/>RoHS compliant</td></tr><tr><td>Warranty</td><td>Lifetime warranty on the case shell</td></tr></tbody></table></div></div>', '2023-05-12 18:07:33', 'The CXT1000 is a hard case that fits all your Fluke test tools and accessories. Configure the diced foam interior to store, protect, and carry your test tools.', NULL, NULL),
(51, 'Fluke C75 Accessory Case', 'Fluke C75 Accessory Case', NULL, '', '', '13', 13, 11, '', 'c75_c_nr-1453-1500x1000.jpg', '', '', NULL, '', '', '<div id=\"fluke-product-display-resources\"><div aria-multiselectable=\"true\" class=\"panel-group\" id=\"resources-accordion\" role=\"tablist\"><div class=\"panel panel-default\"><div class=\"panel-heading\" id=\"resources-data-sheets-title\" role=\"tab\"><h4 class=\"panel-title\"> <a aria-controls=\"resources-data-sheets-list\" aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"collapsed\" href=\"#resources-data-sheets-list\" role=\"button\"> Data sheets (1) </a></h4></div><div aria-labelledby=\"resources-data-sheets-title\" class=\"panel-collapse collapse\" id=\"resources-data-sheets-list\" role=\"tabpanel\"><div class=\"panel-body\"><ul class=\"resources-data-sheets-list\"><li class=\"resources-fluke-c75-accessory-case-item\"> <a class=\"event-fluke-c75-accessory-case\" href=\"/en-in/product/accessories/cases/fluke-c75/ds\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Fluke C75 Accessory Case | Data sheets</a></li></ul></div></div></div><div class=\"panel panel-default\"><div class=\"panel-heading\" id=\"resources-register-products-title\" role=\"tab\"><h4 class=\"panel-title\"> <a aria-controls=\"resources-register-products-list\" aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"collapsed\" href=\"#resources-register-products-list\" role=\"button\"> Register products </a></h4></div><div aria-labelledby=\"resources-register-products-title\" class=\"panel-collapse collapse\" id=\"resources-register-products-list\" role=\"tabpanel\"><div class=\"panel-body\"><ul class=\"resources-register-products-list\"><li class=\"resources-register-products-item\"> <a class=\"event-register-product\" href=\"https://my.fluke.com/en-US/register-product/\">Register product</a></li></ul></div></div></div></div></div>', 1, NULL, NULL, '', 0, 'Having the right accessories on-hand is important to make measurements quickly and safely. The C75 Accessory Case is a zippered carrying case d