(56, 'Fluke Pack30 Professional Tool Backpack', 'Fluke Pack30 Professional Tool Backpack', NULL, '', '', '13', 13, 11, '', 'Fluke-pack30-backpack.jpg,Fluke-pack30-depth.jpg,Fluke-pack30-side-pocket.jpg,fluke-backpack-front-pocket.jpg,fluke-pack30-tool-view.jpg', '', '', NULL, '', '', '<div id=\"fluke-product-display-resources\"><div aria-multiselectable=\"true\" class=\"panel-group\" id=\"resources-accordion\" role=\"tablist\"><div class=\"panel panel-default\"><div class=\"panel-heading\" id=\"resources-flyer-forms-title\" role=\"tab\"><h4 class=\"panel-title\"> <a aria-controls=\"resources-flyer-forms-list\" aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"collapsed\" href=\"#resources-flyer-forms-list\" role=\"button\"> Flyer_forms (1) </a></h4></div><div aria-labelledby=\"resources-flyer-forms-title\" class=\"panel-collapse collapse\" id=\"resources-flyer-forms-list\" role=\"tabpanel\"><div class=\"panel-body\"><ul class=\"resources-flyer-forms-list\"><li class=\"resources-flyer-forms-item\"> <a class=\"event-flyer-forms\" href=\"https://dam-assets.fluke.com/s3fs-public/6010944_0000_ENG_A_W.PDF?ARECfUt4ycs5KClq_QMxHkOy492gskB_\">Fluke Pack30 Flyer</a></li></ul></div></div></div><div class=\"panel panel-default\"><div class=\"panel-heading\" id=\"resources-data-sheets-title\" role=\"tab\"><h4 class=\"panel-title\"> <a aria-controls=\"resources-data-sheets-list\" aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"collapsed\" href=\"#resources-data-sheets-list\" role=\"button\"> Data sheets (1) </a></h4></div><div aria-labelledby=\"resources-data-sheets-title\" class=\"panel-collapse collapse\" id=\"resources-data-sheets-list\" role=\"tabpanel\"><div class=\"panel-body\"><ul class=\"resources-data-sheets-list\"><li class=\"resources-fluke-pack30-professional-tool-backpack-item\"> <a class=\"event-fluke-pack30-professional-tool-backpack\" href=\"/en-in/product/accessories/cases/fluke-pack30/ds\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Fluke Pack30 Professional Tool Backpack | Data sheets</a></li></ul></div></div></div><div class=\"panel panel-default\"><div class=\"panel-heading\" id=\"resources-register-products-title\" role=\"tab\"><h4 class=\"panel-title\"> <a aria-controls=\"resources-register-products-list\" aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"collapsed\" href=\"#resources-register-products-list\" role=\"button\"> Register products </a></h4></div><div aria-labelledby=\"resources-register-products-title\" class=\"panel-collapse collapse\" id=\"resources-register-products-list\" role=\"tabpanel\"><div class=\"panel-body\"><ul class=\"resources-register-products-list\"><li class=\"resources-register-products-item\"> <a class=\"event-register-product\" href=\"https://my.fluke.com/en-US/register-product/\">Register product</a></li></ul></div></div></div></div></div>', 1, NULL, NULL, '', 0, 'Designed for professional electricians and tradesmenThe Fluke Pack30 backpack for professional electricians and tradesmen is rugged yet weighs less than 6.5 pounds. It is built with durable high-quality polyester and features over 30 heavy-duty pockets for storing and carrying your tools to the next job. Three main storage compartments for test tools, hand tools, and a 12” laptop/tablet; a fourth smaller molded pocket for protection of smaller items. Rugged waterproof molded bottom offers protection from the elements and keeps the backpack standing for convenient access to tools. See why the Fluke Backpack is the number one choice for carrying tools.Ergonomically Designed Padding in the back for comfort and lumbar supportAdjustable chest strap for even weight distribution and increased comfortWeighs only 6.5 poundsInterior Features Clips, brackets and straps on the outside of the Fluke Pack30 for frequently used tools such as tape rolls, measuring tapes, voltage detectorsStores, organizes and protects test equipment, hand tools, safety glasses, and personal items like keys, wallet and phoneSpecial pocket for tablet PCs and laptops 12 inches (30 cm) wide or smallerDurability Built with durable high-quality polyester and plastic bottom baseRugged, waterproof bottom base protects tools, keeping the backpack upright for easy access to toolsStandard one-year warranty; extendable to 2 years through product registration within 45 days of purchase *Tools shown not included with the Fluke Pack30 * Register product online within 45 days of purchase to extend warranty to two years. See forms.fluke.com/register-your-product to sign up. Look on the back of the “country of origin” tag inside the backpack for the date code; enter this date code in the Serial Number field. Extended warranty applicable in U.S.A. only.', '<div id=\"specification_content\"><div class=\"clickability\"><table><thead><tr><th colspan=\"2\">Key Features</th></tr><tr><td valign=\"top\">Dimensions</td><td valign=\"top\">20 in x 13 in x 9.25 in (50.8 cm x 33 cm x 23.5 cm)</td></tr><tr><td valign=\"top\">Net weight</td><td valign=\"top\">5 pounds (2.26 kg)</td></tr><tr><td valign=\"top\">Storage compartments</td><td valign=\"top\">1 central storage compartment<br/>1 front compartment<br/>2 side compartments<br/>1 top compartment<br/>1 12 inch (30 cm) back pocket</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\"><small>Tools shown not included with the Fluke Pack30</small></td></tr></thead></table></div></div>', '2023-05-12 18:07:33', 'Designed for professional electricians and tradesmenThe Fluke Pack30 backpack for professional electricians and tradesmen is rugged yet weighs less than 6.5 pounds. It is built with durable high-quality polyester and features over 30 heavy-duty pockets for storing and carrying your tools to the next job. Three main storage compartments for test tools, hand tools, and a 12” laptop/tablet; a fourth smaller molded pocket for protection of smaller items. Rugged waterproof molded bottom offers protection from the elements and keeps the backpack standing for convenient access to tools. See why the Fluke Backpack is the number one choice for carrying tools.Ergonomically Designed Padding in the back for comfort and lumbar supportAdjustable chest strap for even weight distribution and increased comfortWeighs only 6.5 poundsInterior Features Clips, brackets and straps on the outside of the Fluke Pack30 for frequently used tools such as tape rolls, measuring tapes, voltage detectorsStores, organizes and protects test equipment, hand tools, safety glasses, and personal items like keys, wallet and phoneSpecial pocket for tablet PCs and laptops 12 inches (30 cm) wide or smallerDurability Built with durable high-quality polyester and plastic bottom baseRugged, waterproof bottom base protects tools, keeping the backpack upright for easy access to toolsStandard one-year warranty; extendable to 2 years through product registration within 45 days of purchase *Tools shown not included with the Fluke Pack30 * Register product online within 45 days of purchase to extend warranty to two years. See forms.fluke.com/register-your-product to sign up. Look on the back of the “country of origin” tag inside the backpack for the date code; enter this date code in the Serial Number field. Extended warranty applicable in U.S.A. only.', NULL, NULL),
