ns are compatible with a wide range of Fluke test probes and clips. Some often-used probe tips include:TP175 TwistGuard™ Test ProbesTP220 SureGrip™ Industrial Test ProbesAC220 SureGrip™ Alligator ClipsAC285 SureGrip™ Alligator ClipsAC280 SureGrip™ Hook ClipsTP1 SlimReach™ Test ProbesAC283 SureGrip™ Pincer Clips', NULL, NULL),
