></tr><tr><td>Safety</td><td>CAT III, 600 V</td></tr><tr><td>Maximum voltage</td><td>600 V</td></tr><tr class=\"head\"><td colspan=\"2\">Mechanical and General Specifications</td></tr><tr><td>Warranty</td><td>1 year</td></tr><tr><td>Battery life</td><td>9 V, 60 h</td></tr><tr><td>Maximum conductor diameter</td><td>30 mm<br/>2 x 25 mm</td></tr><tr><td>Output cable length</td><td>1.6 m</td></tr><tr><td>Shrouded banana plugs</td><td>Yes</td></tr></tbody></table></div></div>', '2023-05-12 18:07:33', 'Fluke current clamps extend the current ranges of Fluke tools. The Fluke i1010 AC/DC current clamp is highly reliable, measures 1 A to 1000 A and provides accurate current reading without breaking the circuit. This clamp measures both ac and dc current with a large jaw, battery-powered Hall-effect probe that gives access to difficult to reach areas. Compatible with most Fluke multimeters.', NULL, NULL),
