td>1 A to 5 A</td><td>NA</td></tr><tr><td>5 A to 10 A</td><td>Unspecified</td></tr><tr><td>10 A to 20 A</td><td>2°</td></tr><tr><td>20 A to 40 A</td><td>2°</td></tr><tr><td>40 A to 400 A</td><td>1.5°</td></tr><tr><td rowspan=\"2\">Typical bandwidth</td><td><b>40 A Range</b></td><td>5 Hz - 10 kHz</td></tr><tr><td>400 A Range</td><td>5 Hz - 10 kHz</td></tr><tr><td rowspan=\"2\">Output level(s)</td><td><b>40 A Range</b></td><td>10 mV/A</td></tr><tr><td>400 A Range</td><td>1 mV/A</td></tr><tr><td rowspan=\"3\">Crest factor</td><td><b>40 A Range</b></td><td>≤ 3</td></tr><tr><td>400 A Range</td><td>≤ 3 to 300 A</td></tr><tr><td> </td><td>≤ 2.5 to 400 A</td></tr><tr class=\"head\"><td colspan=\"3\">Safety Specifications</td></tr><tr><td>Safety</td><td colspan=\"2\">CAT IV, 600 V, CAT III, 1000 V</td></tr><tr><td>Maximum non-destructive current</td><td colspan=\"2\">1000 V AC</td></tr><tr class=\"head\"><td colspan=\"3\">Mechanical and General Specifications</td></tr><tr><td>Warranty</td><td colspan=\"2\">1 year</td></tr><tr><td>Maximum conductor size</td><td colspan=\"2\">32 mm (1.25 inches)</td></tr><tr><td>Output cable length</td><td colspan=\"2\">2.5 m (8.2 ft)</td></tr><tr><td>BNC adapter</td><td colspan=\"2\">Yes</td></tr><tr><td>Dimensions</td><td colspan=\"2\">150 x 70 x 30 mm</td></tr><tr><td>Weight</td><td colspan=\"2\">114 g</td></tr></tbody></table></div></div>', '2023-05-12 18:07:33', 'Fluke current clamps extend the current ranges of digital multimeters, power quality analyzers, and portable oscilloscopes and are available for both AC and AC/DC environments. The Fluke i400s is specially designed to offer maximum utility in a compact shape and is the only current clamp available with a CAT IV 600 V / CAT III 1000 V safety rating.', NULL, NULL),
(166, 'Fluke i200 AC Current Clamp', 'Fluke i200 AC Current Clamp', NULL, '', '', '13', 13, 13, '', 'fluke-i200-01b-s1500x1000.jpg?t5Iyjw9MAJLAaIW.gEoXBfF7nG1YWdaJ,i200-01s-1500x1000.jpg', '', '', NULL, '', '', '<div id=\"fluke-product-display-resources\"><div aria-multiselectable=\"true\" class=\"panel-group\" id=\"resources-accordion\" role=\"tablist\"><div class=\"panel panel-default\"><div class=\"panel-heading\" id=\"resources-manuals-title\" role=\"tab\"><h4 class=\"panel-title\"> <a aria-controls=\"resources-manuals-list\" aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"collapsed\" href=\"#resources-manuals-list\" role=\"button\"> Manuals (1) </a></h4></div><div aria-labelledby=\"resources-manuals-title\" class=\"panel-collapse collapse\" id=\"resources-manuals-list\" role=\"tabpanel\"><div class=\"panel-body\"><ul class=\"resources-manuals-list\"><li class=\"resources-manuals-item\"> <a class=\"event-manual\" href=\"https://dam-assets.fluke.com/s3fs-public/i200s___iseng0500.pdf\">i200/i200s | Instruction sheet</a></li></ul></div></div></div><div class=\"panel panel-default\"><div class=\"panel-heading\" id=\"resources-data-sheets-title\" role=\"tab\"><h4 class=\"panel-title\"> <a aria-controls=\"resources-data-sheets-list\" aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"collapsed\" href=\"#resources-data-sheets-list\" role=\"button\"> Data sheets (1) </a></h4></div><div aria-labelledby=\"resources-data-sheets-title\" class=\"panel-collapse collapse\" id=\"resources-data-sheets-list\" role=\"tabpanel\"><div class=\"panel-body\"><ul class=\"resources-data-sheets-list\"><li class=\"resources-fluke-i200-ac-current-clamp-item\"> <a class=\"event-fluke-i200-ac-current-clamp\" href=\"/en-in/product/accessories/current-clamps/fluke-i200/ds\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Fluke i200 AC Current Clamp | Data sheets</a></li></ul></div></div></div><div class=\"panel panel-default\"><div class=\"panel-heading\" id=\"resources-register-products-title\" role=\"tab\"><h4 class=\"panel-title\"> <a ari