s://my.fluke.com/en-US/register-product/\">Register product</a></li></ul></div></div></div></div></div>', 1, NULL, NULL, '', 0, 'Intelligent test probe set with integrated IR temperature sensor designed for Fluke BT521 Battery Analyzer. The BTL21 has a built in LCD display, tri-light LED for pass/fail warning indication, voice count for battery ID and integrated save button. Comes with both long and short probe extenders for use in hard to reach battery cabinets.', NULL, '2023-05-12 18:07:33', 'Intelligent test probe set with integrated IR temperature sensor designed for Fluke BT521 Battery Analyzer. The BTL21 has a built in LCD display, tri-light LED for pass/fail warning indication, voice count for battery ID and integrated save button. Comes with both long and short probe extenders for use in hard to reach battery cabinets.', NULL, NULL),
