eel and nylon construction for use in connecting a Fluke-700HTP-1 or other hydraulic test pump to a unit under test.The Fluke 700HTH-1 allows connection to both a Fluke pressure module and a calibration unit under test from a Fluke 700HTP-1 hydraulic test pump simultaneously. 700HTH-1 is compatible with water and non-corrosive oil.', NULL, NULL),
